<title>Configurar SyncTex</title>
<p>Para engadir compatibilidade para SyncTex débense instalar os seguintes paquetes:</p>
<list>
  <item>
    <p>
      A LaTeX engine with SyncTeX support, such as <app>pdflatex</app>.
    </p>
  </item>
  <item>
    <p>
      A text editor with SyncTeX support, such as <app>gedit</app> with gedit-plugins installed.
    </p>
  </item>
</list>

<p>En <app>gedit</app>, active o complemento SyncTex:</p>
<steps>
   <item>
    <p>Prema na lapela <guiseq><gui>Editar</gui><gui>Preferencias</gui><gui>Engadidos</gui></guiseq>.</p>
   </item>
   <item>
    <p>Marque <gui>SyncTex</gui>.</p>
   </item>
</steps>
